thread.title: Jet H.

author: Jet H.
title: Jet H.
text: We were looking for a UI/UX designer at a reasonable rate since we are a small start-up and Toptal was able to connect us with Anna. She is incredibly talented and has been instrumental to the success of our product. Toptal truly does find the upper echelon of talent out there and will work with you to make the process of finding the right person for your team and budget exciting, personalized and fruitful in a very short time.
